  → development/Enterprise/Architecture/CIM[Common Information Model (CIM)]

  The WinRM service can be started in → Windows/PowerShell with the → Windows/PowerShell/command-inventory/noun/psRemoting/enable[`enable-psRemoting`] cmdLet.

